{"tid":891372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底香港人識唔撚識分夜訓同唔夠訓？","createTime":"2018-11-06T05:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T01:33:43.000Z","uid":151865,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"40d7c24d52b6f2e0c84f20a16a3233d3be2bd75c","tid":891372,"uid":151865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T05:00:58.000Z","msg":"成日話<span style=\"color: red;\">夜訓</span>對身體唔好 但講黎講去都係<span style=\"color: red;\">睡眠不足</span>既壞處 我夜晚4點訓都係夜訓架 但我日日訓撚到第朝12點 都有8個鐘 咁我又到底算唔算夜訓呢？其實有無科學研究話每日過某一個鐘數訓係訓幾多都無用？"},{"pid":"9c90c58f858baf9d5760828533f307982f55b41c","tid":891372,"uid":20809,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T05:11:11.000Z","msg":"中醫撚會話d器官唔知幾點又要休息之類<br />\n<br />\n我覺得睇你係咪固定時間訓同訓幾多個鐘，冇分咩夜訓"},{"pid":"4dda140875527d24c35c0bcb739479962f4e1713","tid":891372,"uid":66945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T05:16:18.000Z","msg":"我諗好睇你個生理時鐘係點"},{"pid":"c594896c9a24c22b3254513612813af28653c9ca","tid":891372,"uid":15483,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T05:17:24.000Z","msg":"不過我都覺得早睡早起同夜睡夜起好明顯唔同<br />\n<br />\n有冇專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0954421954804115649ee44fe4cd9302664fe72","tid":891372,"uid":69125,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T05:18:51.000Z","msg":"夜訓其實只係等於o係香港行外國(e.g.歐洲)嘅時間表,應該都唔會有問題啦,正常都唔會有人話外國人咁生活有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60308896d1cfb24a56788c1ab85b9b8e549ea959","tid":891372,"uid":180402,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T05:51:33.000Z","msg":"個人覺得夜睡夜起最舒服"},{"pid":"296028badac707d1c1b8194a2311de4a2aa19459","tid":891372,"uid":209890,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"你黑眼圈會越黎越大<br />\n因為身體排毒最佳時間係夜晚<br />\n唔夠訓既副作用係立即發生<br />\n夜訓副作用要好長遠時間發生"},{"pid":"3e0c55c04a4be2cde75bd28408d01489c5414300","tid":891372,"uid":2404,"like":0,