身，仲有上面影響嘅因素。<br />\n明白嘅人會好回味大學嗰種訓醒之後極精神，可以即刻彈起身嗰種感覺，就會愛上每日定時睡眠。"},{"pid":"02538d275d56c9017492ef8e3bb9bcc696ad2b0e","tid":891372,"uid":32826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:32:15.000Z","msg":"其實不學無術就唔撚好話咩香港人識唔識點啦"},{"pid":"9bf5bbeab11240284a210db45ead49c9c9ba34f9","tid":891372,"uid":188174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"香港人識唔識分  瞓 同  訓？"},{"pid":"fcacd4eac70a5a6ec57cabdc5795a84b82f3a57f","tid":891372,"uid":65400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bf5bbeab11240284a210db45ead49c9c9ba34f9","tid":891372,"uid":188174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"香港人識唔識分  瞓 同  訓？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"5 sick"},{"pid":"98aa73c28b4d86e790c3ca6e1b8dd9e4e6723b29","tid":891372,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54aef5b30917b15cfe4316229cc441295c398385","tid":891372,"uid":84511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T06:54:12.000Z","msg":"重點係睡眠質量<br />\n激素影響睡眠週期，只有深度睡眠先正。<br />\n所以你間房一定要窗簾好勁，成間房都夠黑，而且保證無人影響你訓教，例如老母收衫出出入入，樓上樓下裝修。<br />\n所以朝早訓教係無問題，不過通常你朝早都有嘢做，例如一個星期總可能有一日要提早起身，仲有上面影響嘅因素。<br />\n明白嘅人會好回味大學嗰種訓醒之後極精神，可以即刻彈起身嗰種感覺，就會愛上每日定時睡眠。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ef39cc25581544f7e14a08341347dce9d2bef4","tid":891372,"uid":130858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce7a460f64a82e27e4619a09c42575df323c70a5","tid":891372,"uid":57524,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"7654670d103d53e43a31fad7de90a58c02b83e4e","tid":891372,"uid":100230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc95056b7fb976f3ced53b08cb2f0595f1de2453","tid":891372,"uid":82482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy"